    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="597804831">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-597804831" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-597804831" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="597804831">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/marukon/">丸子君</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-11-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">《昔话》在内容上虽然比《物语》丰富，但后者更有幽玄之感。仿佛作者本身隐藏在叙述之事的后面而尽力白描，继承了《今昔物语》中所含野性勃勃之美的地方。值得一提的是许多传说与唐代志怪笔记继续如出一辙，这也算是一个较好的学术研究切入点。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="602753932">
